headline: Smurfit Westrock announces permanent closure of a paper machine at La Tuque mill
summary: DUBLIN, February 09, 2026--Smurfit Westrock plc (NYSE: SW, LSE: SWR) today announced it will permanently close one of the paper machines at its La Tuque, Quebec, mill. The machine’s annual production capacity of 127,000 tons of solid bleached sulfate (SBS) has faced ongoing scale and cost challenges.

headline: Smurfit Westrock to Report Q4 Earnings: What's in Store for the Stock?
summary: SW heads into Q4 earnings with modest revenue growth expected, as stable packaging demand offsets weak volumes in Europe.
